{"title":"Continuum. Terapia endovascular en Ictus isquemico agudo-2025","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Neurología/Continuum. Terapia endovascular en Ictus isquemico agudo-2025.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Terapia Endovascular en Ictus\\NIsquémico Agudo (EVT)","guid":"oiTXhPybSIkKP72SO-RTAw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"RESUMEN","guid":"59RWGc1BXZ6KsRstGVwqOQ","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"📌 Objetivo","guid":"MxyD8bKR7iWof9aAXSda_Q","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"🔹 Mejorar el tratamiento del ictus isquémico\\Nagudo más grave y discapacitante.","guid":"JGlbXpSTT1BxBbuHxyWDlg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"🔹 Resumir innovaciones\\Nrecientes y futuras en EVT.","guid":"Jn3SLHiBnYq32s_QbuGBvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"1","text":"📌 Últimos\\Navances","guid":"AFvR4rL2-S4B8XbkGtE_kw","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"✅ Optimización\\Ndel manejo","guid":"6kvaFQs95-_QUHcziBeL2g","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"• 🚑 Prehospitalario → Mejoras en la ruta de derivación.","guid":"WSYoJTWtHY6gaOHHmZHQQg","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"• 🏥 Intrahospitalario → Mayor eficiencia en cribado.","guid":"oSXG3L0x60rFxVJkDySNiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"✅ Expansión de\\Nindicaciones","guid":"mJlSnkzV2EwoNyk2GyR5XA","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"• 🧠 Pacientes sin imagen avanzada.","guid":"UNrpd4wQxFiEWlVZLX_yOw","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"• 🏥 Infartos con núcleo isquémico grande.","guid":"VgUUomQNDUxFFHR0znTybA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"9","text":"• 🔬 Oclusiones más distales.","guid":"gWejAGAqg5-sCcMJbC_cjg","children":[]}]},{"id":"13","parent":"5","text":"✅ Innovación\\Ntecnológica","guid":"BGow_ZKKwfz_mXjdKcU_0Q","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"• 🛠️ Nuevos dispositivos para trombectomía.","guid":"ucGO0o7UyF737LCic5iXYw","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"13","text":"• 🔄 Mejoras en la reperfusión y resultados clínicos.","guid":"NmtMIgreiMeWrkri1mIN1Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"16","parent":"5","text":"✅ Impacto en la\\Norganización sanitaria","guid":"II1n2j_5LUikYDF4BqQjMA","children":[{"id":"17","parent":"16","text":"• 🏨 Transformación de los patrones de referencia.","guid":"z4nNQdQCx1lr6tQJlUZN3A","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"16","text":"• 🎖️ Nuevos modelos de acreditación hospitalaria.","guid":"YZ19Efe8_cr_P9vLuKtCBg","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"16","text":"• 👩 ⚕️ Cambios en la práctica neurointervencionista.","guid":"_oplq21EyVSWxcNAKuZCqQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"20","parent":"1","text":"📌 Puntos\\Nesenciales","guid":"Iigp1plqMF93tdbvCmEptQ","children":[{"id":"21","parent":"20","text":"🔸 Estado actual de la EVT y su impacto.","guid":"3knRCsOrRt8cP0JJ1u0z-A","children":[]},{"id":"22","parent":"20","text":"🔸 Ilustración con 3 casos clínicos de oclusión de ACM-M1 en pacientes jóvenes.","guid":"jpw7s-89M4pMjBNMjAHa6A","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"20","text":"🔸 Diferencias en evaluación, toma de decisiones y tratamiento.","guid":"3kAI-hfjr8jZtrG0EA4Fhw","children":[]}]},{"id":"24","parent":"1","text":"CONTEXTO","guid":"P0Pa4OYFhoTaEiSb-3EAEA","children":[{"id":"25","parent":"24","text":"📢 Desde los ensayos clínicos aleatorizados en 2015, EVT\\Nes el estándar de atención en pacientes seleccionados.","guid":"mQspIwetRJ1gLt4EZKqghQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"24","text":"📈 El ritmo de avances en EVT ha acelerado significativamente.","guid":"gI_EvNt20HF5-D9T71comQ","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"24","text":"🔄 Cambios\\Nestructurales en:","guid":"KrKoc5yqq66hU2E0QPBjvg","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"• ⚡ Sistemas de\\Natención del ictus.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"• 🏥 Prácticas\\Nneurointervencionistas.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"• 🎖️ Acreditación\\Nhospitalaria.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"0","text":"Estado Actual de la Terapia\\NEndovascular en Ictus Isquémico (EVT)","guid":"13OvkywYZkUe6-JNC23tYg","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"1️⃣ Evolución\\Nde EVT","guid":"wAODPbkledNaJf8N-ejU2g","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"🔹 2013 → Ensayos clínicos negativos.","guid":"NgHIpQtMbvGoyLLoarK6Wg","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"🔹 2015 → Ensayos clínicos positivos → EVT se establece como estándar de tratamiento.","guid":"fnLdqIpUnVCk3Zr4GjI-5g","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"🔹 NNT (Número Necesario a Tratar) EVT = 3-5 → Gran impacto en recuperación funcional.","guid":"Qq67hk9ZcRSZfV48WtqUuw","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"32","text":"• EVT (NNT = 3-5) vs. ICP en IAM\\Ncon elevación ST","guid":"5BuHYPuScl9YS11QfbfopQ","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• NNT 45 → prevenir mortalidad.","guid":"px29llnJiMKTd0xlta5EsA","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• NNT 22 → prevenir reinfarto.","guid":"huB9lRnRorSHcbRYraKwFw","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"32","text":"🔹 EVT cambia el manejo\\Ndel ictus de gran vaso","guid":"qMulC8yObSVP7d529Y-bug","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• ➡️ Enfoque de consenso en neurología.","guid":"NfLLaK_sDWjvvZKgf1DEuw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"• ➡️ Neurología como especialidad clave en neurointervención.","guid":"AbLRzNEejBFHBXnDxeuXGg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"31","text":"2️⃣ Indicaciones\\NActuales","guid":"NTLJDRnmhVe8X_MGxKS8AA","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"✅ rTPA IV en pacientes elegibles.","guid":"fiWYQh3wKqJ99qaEFGllAQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"✅ EVT en oclusión proximal de gran\\Nvaso sin infarto extenso.","guid":"eYSIS-1oM5vrW5ZNip9m2Q","children":[{"id":"45","parent":"44","text":"• Ventana 0-6 h → ASPECTS >6 (TAC simple).","guid":"ydqsRdaeUyG9aG6l0TW7GQ","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"44","text":"• Ventana 6-24 h → TAC perfusión / RM.","guid":"ZlXgHD4qovVeI0I4-duHEw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"47","parent":"31","text":"3️⃣ Caso Clínico\\N(Caso 3-1)","guid":"0yoBxOw9DwU9wgWz-vQd3A","children":[{"id":"48","parent":"47","text":"👨 ⚕️ Paciente: 64 años, síntomas → hemiparesia derecha, desviación de mirada izquierda, afasia global.","guid":"a9jEmPAC3SOdb7LLv9x0VA","children":[]},{"id":"49","parent":"47","text":"🕒 Última vez bien: 3 horas antes.","guid":"6eWZWoXO1Cr1PVSJczhQjg","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"47","text":"🩺 Antecedente: Fibrilación auricular sin anticoagulación.","guid":"dkGGT-qUVZOOfkj_dt3TJg","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"47","text":"📋 Evaluación:","guid":"-_yMjUVlSGiBKCsyqKrvjQ","children":[{"id":"52","parent":"51","text":"🖥️ TAC simple → ASPECTS 8, signos iniciales en núcleo lentiforme izquierdo.","guid":"tz4S--85CFPaQua75hyDzA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"51","text":"🩸 AngioTAC → Oclusión ACM-M1 izquierda.","guid":"MugqiKQnPD0sZfJIL5seJw","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"51","text":"💉 Manejo: rTPA IV + EVT.","guid":"SkjTC_GnffqHx8_BUHYxcA","children":[]}]},{"id":"55","parent":"47","text":"📷 EVT (DSA):","guid":"gvMX6Gq6EwQgtM7MRJYhHg","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"✔️ Confirmación de oclusión ACM-M1.","guid":"No2zBsE2ZgyMKJnlWe8wcA","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"55","text":"✔️ Reperfusión completa con un solo pase de aspiración.","guid":"MkvvJBmdHz8k2QjenU5Fcw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"55","text":"✔️ TAC control → sin nuevas lesiones isquémicas.","guid":"aN9wa8GaeXxojsTIXnR3Dw","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"✔️ Mejoría clínica sustancial post-EVT.","guid":"O6beN9z0mwt9gB4HoPqTxA","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"47","text":"💡 Comentario","guid":"NJW2umCEGFvY-RIFeSqCTw","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"🔹 EVT rápida en pacientes sin progresión isquémica\\Nprecoz puede lograr recuperación funcional casi completa.","guid":"x4nZcv9AF20UCWVKgYarqQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"62","parent":"31","text":"4️⃣ Crecimiento\\Nde EVT","guid":"lynpidrcoWAgRINQkeFqzw","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"📈 Aumento en:","guid":"jMiUSgOhG28fbc_q3XaCdg","children":[{"id":"64","parent":"63","text":"✅ Número de procedimientos.","guid":"oimIoQ5XlTw-sAhjm_r4pw","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"63","text":"✅ Número de hospitales con EVT \\N(188 hospitales/año en EE.UU. 2012-2016).","guid":"F-kws2wM4nqlLJ8qi2AjUA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"63","text":"✅ Volumen de casos mejora resultados\\N(↓4% mortalidad por cada 10 procedimientos).","guid":"QQPAqg_cR04jlRkH0yLoZQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"62","text":"✅ Resultados en el mundo real\\Nsimilares a ensayos clínicos.","guid":"JNhbkzplZkS7dE17qIchTg","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Independencia\\Nfuncional 90 días:","guid":"_ySfmy2G33NDwwwVJ1sIRw","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"• EVT → 55%.","guid":"LqFAv-fxyLsf380mnIBMQA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"• Sin EVT → 26.5%.","guid":"5-9AWjaqJawtMIdvNzXuYg","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"• HIC sintomática → 2-6%, comparable con rTPA IV solo.","guid":"c31pf3w0pV51DDlkbKPFAA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"31","text":"5️⃣ Retos y\\NLimitaciones","guid":"woRfrtKNgudm2CTXTPMVLg","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"❌ Acceso\\Ndesigual a EVT","guid":"4rNag1JMOaSRTZ49L6Joag","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• 🏥 Rural → <30% pacientes tratados en hospitales con EVT.","guid":"eE7naHtKBAa37qpsFO35hw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"• 🚑 Menos probabilidad de recibir EVT, incluso con traslado disponible.","guid":"YfVKMEUqGvjG15hE_ZbKQg","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"72","text":"❌ Carga laboral creciente para\\Nneurointervencionistas","guid":"iCmCwQjtQaA76beUsGu4cQ","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• ⏰ Más turnos de urgencia, menos procedimientos electivos.","guid":"QpYrBAR0-yEGUGkPzqXSbA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"• ⚖️ Desbalance entre oferta/demanda de especialistas.","guid":"cauE8fZ6XseT-Zq1KjqouQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"79","parent":"72","text":"❌ Desafíos en\\Nformación y acreditación","guid":"Nd6ipcVsZGXf8V42Db9G3w","children":[{"id":"80","parent":"79","text":"• 📚 Falta de un sistema uniforme de certificación en neurointervención.","guid":"tcyRq4S0pUTEQP-udJ8QCA","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"79","text":"• 🧠 Creciente interés de neurólogos en EVT.","guid":"3XhWYr-ij8n6_aqSVqe8QA","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"79","text":"• 📌 Propuestas:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Formación de neurólogos vasculares como EVT-only.","guid":"KTeigmp5Z17JFYSaAFMMPw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Incluir cardiólogos e intervencionistas radiólogos en EVT.","guid":"sLBnPfO9rSI3iXfWY1bQxg","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"0","text":"Investigaciones en\\NCurso en EVT","guid":"Q6MuHZTWkCQ3z9i7yZ0YZw","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"1️⃣ Optimización del\\NManejo Prehospitalario","guid":"YOTudXFlaa4fhKVuuYU-CQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"📌 Importancia: EVT es altamente dependiente del tiempo → derivar\\Npacientes directo a hospitales EVT-capaces podría mejorar los resultados.","guid":"l5eWXp5gwA-fmslwV1b6gw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"✅ Estrategias:","guid":"puWMJ6LLrOktOlur9b-kbQ","children":[{"id":"89","parent":"88","text":"• 🚑 Bypass prehospitalario → Basado en escalas de ictus (ej. RACE).","guid":"nrlPCTgW-s90bPHS59Op5w","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"88","text":"• ⏳ Reglas de\\Ntransporte:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• ≤ 15 min adicionales de traslado → ir a hospital EVT.","guid":"CPVAmWG6Qd77aNY-w7gKFQ","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"•  15 min adicionales → ir al hospital más cercano para rTPA IV.","guid":"f1snC69U0L2ZapF0IT6JkA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"93","parent":"86","text":"🔬 Evidencia\\N(RACECAT Trial -\\NEspaña)","guid":"knjtd9Ab-jUWOY39GYVgHw","children":[{"id":"94","parent":"93","text":"• Comparó traslado a centro primario vs. traslado directo a hospital EVT.","guid":"sqlgO7vuGriu_OH1a2YQSw","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"93","text":"• Resultados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"96","parent":"95","text":"• 🚑 Pacientes en hospital primario → Más rTPA IV, menos EVT.","guid":"UrEFYlGD4cTLui5Qa-z2Ig","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"95","text":"• 🔄 65% requerían traslado a centro EVT.","guid":"XxVy1BBmoRinHmpuHRdelA","children":[]},{"id":"98","parent":"95","text":"• ❌ No hubo diferencia en discapacidad a 90 días.","guid":"GW13NXxFTuIqV8RnTb0cWA","children":[]}]},{"id":"99","parent":"93","text":"• Limitaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"100","parent":"99","text":"• ⏳ Tiempos de traslado en España más cortos que en EE.UU.","guid":"Ius3RGIBqAt4DXkFHfPmMg","children":[]},{"id":"101","parent":"99","text":"• 🚑 Mejora en diagnóstico prehospitalario → Nuevas tecnologías en desarrollo (ultrasonido, impedancia eléctrica).","guid":"pRfSqW_w0swomTr4jeGkxA","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"99","text":"• 🏥 Unidades móviles de ictus → Alternativa para evitar retrasos en tratamiento.","guid":"fuPY8vD9VUjMTBnim-BUPA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"85","text":"2️⃣ Simplificación y Reducción de\\NImágenes Preprocedimiento","guid":"GipPmOa5eLZ8u8uhWRnp1w","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"📌 Objetivo: Minimizar estudios innecesarios y acelerar EVT.","guid":"zRPLf1bucYAwcSqYSPzq1g","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"✅ Guías AHA/ASA:","guid":"AD-9cO9wMNqqsCvZAi_OYg","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• 0-6 h → TAC simple + AngioTAC.","guid":"HqDI7Wy1iVkr06-ocmCXlg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• 6-24 h → TAC perfusión (CTP) o RM.","guid":"8Yh1DB8axZpmlnbndB5E4g","children":[]}]},{"id":"108","parent":"103","text":"🚨 Problemas con TAC\\Nperfusión (CTP)","guid":"o130zXwoLwuatxcIsMflTg","children":[{"id":"109","parent":"108","text":"❌ Limitada disponibilidad → 70% hospitales no realizan CTP.","guid":"lPNlSsEvf4ovfVXIWvATFw","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"108","text":"❌ 25% de estudios inutilizables → Movimiento del paciente.","guid":"OlRe7qbwdIMQp6XUyustnw","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"108","text":"❌ Mayor retraso en EVT → Diferencia de 20 min en estudios comparativos.","guid":"RAM2dhsX_jbHkZNookOb7g","children":[]},{"id":"112","parent":"108","text":"❌ Menor tasa de EVT → Uso rutinario de CTP podría subtratar pacientes.","guid":"-CAiyL0AlBY_2OUcuZdZEQ","children":[]},{"id":"113","parent":"108","text":"❌ Inexactitud en identificación de núcleo isquémico y penumbra → Fluctuaciones en flujo sanguíneo pueden sobreestimar o subestimar la lesión real.","guid":"k4ftXAeWm41_vV3kpHxmRQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"114","parent":"103","text":"🔬 Evidencia\\Nen Estudios","guid":"HIOy0Cm3U4055qbK4PV4jw","children":[{"id":"115","parent":"114","text":"✅ CLEAR Trial (n=1600, 15 centros) → No hubo diferencias en independencia funcional a 90 días entre pacientes seleccionados con TAC simple vs. CTP.","guid":"wuGiDNZ0MMABlGF3zlNSBg","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"114","text":"✅ MR CLEAN LATE → EVT sin CTP en ventana tardía fue superior a tratamiento médico.","guid":"olzxR7W7Jz6DAiFqAvBDeA","children":[]},{"id":"117","parent":"114","text":"✅ RESILIENT Extend Trial → En curso, evaluando EVT en ventana extendida sin CTP.","guid":"Iv84Y79-hNx4uk5glir1cA","children":[]}]},{"id":"118","parent":"103","text":"📌 Conclusión: TAC simple podría ser suficiente para seleccionar\\Npacientes en ventana tardía, reduciendo retrasos en EVT.","guid":"FXFtSl2Xu6GBsxelp9Dlfw","children":[]}]},{"id":"119","parent":"85","text":"3️⃣ Omisión de\\NTrombolisis IV en EVT","guid":"U_c-sT2kHCZx6TporJ7xmQ","children":[{"id":"120","parent":"119","text":"📌 Pregunta: ¿Es necesario administrar rTPA IV en pacientes que van a EVT?","guid":"L5KGlImx63DB2KEi14WsJw","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"119","text":"✅ Ensayos\\Nclínicos 2020-2021","guid":"P0lhJo3URy6Ee_ELAwFvjg","children":[{"id":"122","parent":"121","text":"• SKIP (Japón, alteplasa 0.6 mg/kg) → No mostró no-inferioridad de EVT solo.","guid":"pIC4eV7bv9k_A-frnEXUoQ","children":[]},{"id":"123","parent":"121","text":"• MR CLEAN NO-IV (Países Bajos, 0.9 mg/kg) → Misma conclusión.","guid":"rh7JRV73nlJuuKa6USH80w","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"121","text":"• SWIFT-DIRECT (Europa/Canadá) → No-inferioridad no demostrada.","guid":"LFjldMMxZOkrMzb8xWX_gA","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"121","text":"• DIRECT-SAFE (Australia) → No-inferioridad no demostrada.","guid":"cOgbnJKpTRt3WeJmp2XZzQ","children":[]},{"id":"126","parent":"121","text":"• DEVT (China) → Finalizado prematuramente por alcanzar objetivo primario.","guid":"VGBXzjOpmToa6DemPxaD6w","children":[]},{"id":"127","parent":"121","text":"• DIRECT-MT (China) → Mostró no-inferioridad de EVT solo.","guid":"-IcK5J3kn75pGXMMfrmfiQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"128","parent":"119","text":"✅ Meta-análisis\\Nreciente","guid":"n4dNJCMm_UTIsDfxWFQzNw","children":[{"id":"129","parent":"128","text":"❌ No demostró no-inferioridad de EVT solo.","guid":"THfsldw_JWKAGaEMR_pZxw","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"128","text":"📉 Tendencia débil a favor de rTPA IV + EVT.","guid":"lAuCDrowwuLIcLQHVwHtmQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"85","text":"📌 Conclusión:","guid":"Q82QNEhrdax1WaiADmpvWw","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"🔹 rTPA IV sigue recomendado en pacientes elegibles, incluso si requerirán EVT.","guid":"5VVjyXxmcM4orD8LU64YWQ","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"✅ Ensayos\\Nrecientes en China","guid":"ofcwyXyPgff1UzQzQWrzQw","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"• BAOCHE (ventana tardía: 6-24 h).","guid":"eNA0DN8uxjlETy4pXnSd9g","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"• ATTENTION (ventana temprana: <12 h).","guid":"MluJenRFF_Kt201JxiFivw","children":[]},{"id":"136","parent":"133","text":"• 📊 Resultados:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"• EVT superior a manejo médico.","guid":"SSP4qbzT4OaMqnET6Lrnmg","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"• mRS 0-3 a 90 días → NNT: 4-4.5.","guid":"hlaWR8_6NBfdBhc-pOMafQ","children":[]},{"id":"139","parent":"136","text":"• Buenos resultados en EVT (≈45%), control muy bajo (≈22%).","guid":"CGr9TAtcNEXI2SaeWCAKYA","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"140","parent":"0","text":"Selección de Tratamiento y\\NExpansión de Indicaciones en EVT","guid":"X6HY3Ae6cJj-XGH0OfRSWA","children":[{"id":"141","parent":"140","text":"1️⃣ EVT en Oclusión\\Nde Arteria Basilar","guid":"bb5IaeMy1b3u3MIWy2GsBg","children":[{"id":"142","parent":"141","text":"📌 Dificultad en obtener evidencia sólida, pese a la eficacia en circulación anterior.","guid":"6o7X_4RmIeowzZt40fDL7A","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"141","text":"📌 Limitaciones en estudios previos → Alto cruce entre brazos de tratamiento.","guid":"dwJYqQ94hxJgePhjnBsjsg","children":[]}]},{"id":"144","parent":"140","text":"2️⃣ EVT en Pacientes\\Ncon NIHSS Bajo","guid":"xcwQ6snXRwDTWWORc4oDzA","children":[{"id":"145","parent":"144","text":"📌 Ensayos previos excluyeron NIHSS <6.","guid":"kHviXVW14xp3jJQuuaTdxQ","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"144","text":"📌 Estudios observacionales\\Nmuestran que:","guid":"62BPGptapZDkqjqeeLmTpA","children":[{"id":"147","parent":"146","text":"• 25% de ictus con NIHSS bajo tienen oclusión de gran vaso.","guid":"c_50nX9SEpR3JgpyCpMsyA","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"146","text":"• Mal pronóstico en deterioro neurológico → Muerte o dependencia en 23-38%.","guid":"VBI52Ju5YIhOOLzr6kwO2A","children":[]}]},{"id":"149","parent":"144","text":"✅ Ensayos\\Nclínicos en curso","guid":"5b5QqtpBtADchYGVzH3aPg","children":[{"id":"150","parent":"149","text":"• ENDOLOW (N. América).","guid":"mNq98ht_OBnHxEZv_8VyDg","children":[]},{"id":"151","parent":"149","text":"• MOSTE (Europa).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"152","parent":"144","text":"📌 Objetivo: Evaluar si EVT mejora resultados en NIHSS bajo vs. manejo médico.","guid":"FbuxmtRxZfnUtQMxvXlGDg","children":[]}]},{"id":"153","parent":"140","text":"3️⃣ EVT en Ventana\\NExtensa (>6h - 24h)","guid":"QaY98HSb8kKUhMNaCNSCwA","children":[{"id":"154","parent":"153","text":"📌 Ensayos\\Nclave (2018):","guid":"-_22vxhntJvs4jJ_hP2-pw","children":[{"id":"155","parent":"154","text":"• DAWN y DEFUSE 3 →\\NEstablecieron EVT hasta 24 h.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"156","parent":"153","text":"✅ Meta-análisis\\NAURORA (6 estudios):","guid":"trpA4WN5UgqEt_rirGKrdA","children":[{"id":"157","parent":"156","text":"• mRS 0-2 a 90 días → 46%\\N(EVT) vs. 19% (control).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"158","parent":"156","text":"• Efecto positivo en todos los subgrupos\\N(despertar, edad ≥80, NIHSS ≥18).","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"159","parent":"153","text":"📌 Nuevas direcciones","guid":"FdYW33HA1F80_cA2IMf_Gw","children":[{"id":"160","parent":"159","text":"• Menos énfasis en tiempo → Más en\\Nimágenes (TAC simple).","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"161","parent":"159","text":"• Estudios reportan EVT efectiva\\Nhasta 44h si imagen favorable.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"162","parent":"140","text":"4️⃣ EVT en Oclusiones\\NDistales (M2 y más allá)","guid":"BFB5Xp2iAq6GlTzOR4iHKQ","children":[{"id":"163","parent":"162","text":"📌 40% de los ictus isquémicos son\\Noclusiones distales/medias.","guid":"o2dU81RV-PfqvwsFsO0I-w","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"162","text":"🔹 Desafíos EVT en\\Nvasos distales","guid":"eGvAU0k9xgEzvTfymHhGsg","children":[{"id":"165","parent":"164","text":"• 🏥 Vasos más pequeños y\\Nfrágiles → Riesgo de lesión.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"166","parent":"164","text":"• 🩺 Déficit clínico menor →\\NBeneficio/riesgo más estrecho.","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"167","parent":"162","text":"✅ Estudios en curso","guid":"lPhR8mScVbM7_8-phfbujQ","children":[{"id":"168","parent":"167","text":"• HERMES (M2 EVT) → Datos\\Npreliminares positivos.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"169","parent":"167","text":"• DISTAL Trial → Evalúa EVT vs. manejo\\Nmédico en oclusiones distales.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"170","parent":"140","text":"5️⃣ EVT en Infarto Extenso\\N(Large Core Infarcts)","guid":"6vcvpyXgdvkfzyxJ1wgL3w","children":[{"id":"171","parent":"170","text":"📌 Tradicionalmente excluidos (ASPECTS <6 o volumen >70 mL).","guid":"2_JsPlo43yENvsHKhtnP5g","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"170","text":"✅ Evidencia emergente","guid":"5YgwMdTiIaV270q9uSmmqQ","children":[{"id":"173","parent":"172","text":"• 📊 Meta-análisis\\NHERMES (ASPECTS 3-5):","guid":"","children":[{"id":"174","parent":"173","text":"• EVT superior a manejo médico (OR 2.0).","guid":"H-eO5fjoY_OFv7bn6j4cpw","children":[]}]},{"id":"175","parent":"172","text":"• 📌 Caso 3-2","guid":"","children":[{"id":"176","parent":"175","text":"• 🔹 Paciente 48 años, ASPECTS 3-4.","guid":"iQfo955XMTByd5PcAqveYA","children":[]},{"id":"177","parent":"175","text":"• 🔹 EVT exitoso → Mejoría funcional significativa.","guid":"dSGYdr-4P3pThkJT72sNyw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"178","parent":"170","text":"✅ Ensayos\\Nclínicos recientes","guid":"3wtRXqEu-nVxsT6vUPS7Ww","children":[{"id":"179","parent":"178","text":"• RESCUE-Japan LIMIT (ASPECTS <6,\\Nvolumen 94-110 mL).","guid":"mR8zLEY--B4rkP9fuwgBpw","children":[{"id":"180","parent":"179","text":"• mRS 0-3 a 90 días → 31% (EVT) vs. 13% (control).","guid":"gwBEJomxK6vsM-SOycWlfw","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"179","text":"• ❌ No ↑ HIC sintomática ni mortalidad.","guid":"14NSbmjr4Pw9_B0GNOG56g","children":[]}]},{"id":"182","parent":"178","text":"• ANGEL-ASPECT (ASPECTS 3-5, volumen 70-100 mL).","guid":"UqCm7D0Ud5DVFZIw_iWz3A","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"178","text":"• SELECT 2 (ASPECTS ≥6, volumen ≥50 mL).","guid":"QLYKZY8VUV2FOapUP793Yw","children":[]}]},{"id":"184","parent":"170","text":"✅ Resultados\\Ngenerales","guid":"4Uh0NOowtlmUV84elHGVKg","children":[{"id":"185","parent":"184","text":"• Mejor pronóstico con EVT (14%-30% buenos resultados).","guid":"EfPUkS2f926g8nF_6GGStA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"184","text":"• HIC sintomática → 6-9% post-EVT.","guid":"YcYcsMPYS8MAR0EH35RTNA","children":[]},{"id":"187","parent":"184","text":"📌 Ensayos en curso (2023)","guid":"o9D2ficjsoYGnaMuJ7W2qA","children":[{"id":"188","parent":"187","text":"• TENSION, LASTE, TESLA → Definir qué subgrupos se benefician más.","guid":"iBjYeFu6Hia3AMO5_L1ZmQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"189","parent":"184","text":"📌 Desafíos futuros","guid":"37OOIwP_vtOhahBIQ9ciKA","children":[{"id":"190","parent":"189","text":"• Evaluar calidad de vida post-EVT en infartos extensos.","guid":"gsFxigusjKeUarE5ynB8qg","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"189","text":"• Determinar si ASPECTS 0-2 vs. 3-5 tienen diferente respuesta a EVT.","guid":"Ql6cr2NWA11fEETisNHJlA","children":[]}]}]}]}]},{"id":"192","parent":"0","text":"Avances en Procedimiento\\Ny Técnica de EVT","guid":"d4gYKEJBP3rCegVkJXeCJQ","children":[{"id":"193","parent":"192","text":"1️⃣ Mejora de\\NDispositivos","guid":"FKFul4G6rDt0nElsfHc76A","children":[{"id":"194","parent":"193","text":"📌 Factor clave en éxito de ensayos de 2015 → Dispositivos iniciales eran poco efectivos y con alto tiempo de procedimiento.","guid":"18cXpBc0H3513dyvi0uSMA","children":[]},{"id":"195","parent":"193","text":"📌 Evolución\\Ntecnológica","guid":"kQn_ewvqZwbsEr4kRN-CWA","children":[{"id":"196","parent":"195","text":"✅ Stent-retrievers → Revolucionaron la trombectomía.","guid":"v4dR-FxRGMpuiDRMxan2DA","children":[]},{"id":"197","parent":"195","text":"✅ Catéteres de aspiración de gran calibre → Mejor recuperación del trombo.","guid":"seM7qGmILYeIRzdgGZo7BQ","children":[]},{"id":"198","parent":"195","text":"🆕 Meta actual: First Pass Effect (FPE)","guid":"4DtCDPKWljk16oPlEa8N6w","children":[]}]},{"id":"199","parent":"193","text":"📌 Reperfusión completa\\N(TICI 3) con un solo pase.","guid":"zr006wf31MNOTzjQCQQXYA","children":[{"id":"200","parent":"199","text":"📌 Beneficios","guid":"UOeZbh0QqegCFBCNfPSljg","children":[{"id":"201","parent":"200","text":"• ⏳ Reducción del tiempo de procedimiento.","guid":"54e5Bljofm-jp7BWxaBxsQ","children":[]},{"id":"202","parent":"200","text":"• 📈 Mejores resultados clínicos.","guid":"Amd5Pj8M2b28l_5eHGbFXA","children":[]}]},{"id":"203","parent":"199","text":"📌 Datos recientes","guid":"DADuymWaSh8Cff2VAKhCDA","children":[{"id":"204","parent":"203","text":"• >50% éxito en FPE.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"205","parent":"203","text":"• >90% éxito en reperfusión final tras múltiples pases.","guid":"B2xqNdTPgK_kdHmM2x1d1g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"206","parent":"192","text":"2️⃣ Resurgimiento del\\NStenting Intracraneal","guid":"gdjhWBUkxNARz2e2V2yi8Q","children":[{"id":"207","parent":"206","text":"📌 Problema: Algunas oclusiones no son solo embólicas, sino por aterosclerosis intracraneal.","guid":"_5DGFLO1_qKVCeYCckpzpA","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"206","text":"📌 Causas","guid":"NsG8EyQ7fT8-nAOqDai4yg","children":[{"id":"209","parent":"208","text":"• 🚶 ♂️ Embolia arteria-arteria.","guid":"M2yl40biBID5pljChQ6j1Q","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"208","text":"• 🚧 Oclusión in situ.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"208","text":"• 🛑 Trombosis de ramas perforantes.","guid":"LVr5vMypZCeidbl464cPDQ","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"208","text":"• ⚠️ Hipoperfusión por estenosis crítica.","guid":"gM-JCiONgrFm15vUVpHJ0g","children":[]}]},{"id":"213","parent":"206","text":"✅ Factores predictivos de\\Naterosclerosis intracraneal","guid":"hvStNWvPbZ3Jf_i7m5WUHQ","children":[{"id":"214","parent":"213","text":"• 🏥 Antecedentes: Diabetes, hipertensión, tabaquismo.","guid":"4QUPTFrqXLn7dTNxv0f6Aw","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"213","text":"• 🏞️ Imagen preprocedimiento → Estenosis en otros vasos intracraneales.","guid":"kEifzH11TuX2nGNssafzoQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"213","text":"• 🤔 NIHSS bajo para la severidad de la oclusión → Sugiere desarrollo de colaterales.","guid":"jXJr5Tqs4Z2J2DRgOIYN6Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"217","parent":"206","text":"📌 Dilema intra-EVT","guid":"64kGIYT6M0VUKFB_ZU5E0w","children":[{"id":"218","parent":"217","text":"🔹 EVT inicial con trombectomía puede revelar estenosis subyacente.","guid":"YG6rFrs0v3WZ5ibnW8u9ug","children":[]},{"id":"219","parent":"217","text":"🔹 Reoclusión tras múltiples intentos → Sospecha de aterosclerosis intracraneal.","guid":"Prn7LM_GcBE5eHtrdWYkZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"220","parent":"206","text":"📌 Caso 3-3","guid":"tdAzHoGmEBNUdGLh9EYDLQ","children":[{"id":"221","parent":"220","text":"👨 ⚕️ Paciente: 53 años, hemiparesia derecha, desviación de mirada izquierda, afasia global.","guid":"ryG-qbHKM2rA7tg6vFp72Q","children":[]},{"id":"222","parent":"220","text":"📌 Hallazgos","guid":"Unzd6_tceR1JBMyUEf1shQ","children":[{"id":"223","parent":"222","text":"• Estenosis intracraneal multifocal.","guid":"atHbmrC2zqyNcGz8Gq2WPg","children":[]},{"id":"224","parent":"222","text":"• Reoclusión tras 2 intentos de trombectomía.","guid":"up0fLuA5htFjqIIEAy8dwg","children":[]}]},{"id":"225","parent":"220","text":"📌 Manejo","guid":"1KKeT9Jtf2isHSReFIsqSA","children":[{"id":"226","parent":"225","text":"✅ EVT con\\NStenting\\NIntracraneal","guid":"h0JyMzAOcAIolrArhzVm1w","children":[{"id":"227","parent":"226","text":"• 📌 Anticoagulación previa (heparina, eptifibatide).","guid":"SFTmgfqfwqJgiO2K6nI8YA","children":[]},{"id":"228","parent":"226","text":"• 📌 Stent de liberación de fármaco.","guid":"ZsS960vBK-kEodQPRSKIlw","children":[]},{"id":"229","parent":"226","text":"• 📌 Éxito con restauración de perfusión MCA-M1.","guid":"4VcQG3R-pUyILehbBbhwnA","children":[]}]},{"id":"230","parent":"225","text":"✅ Manejo post-EVT","guid":"VaT3FlLK5q-DFbxQCnQRkQ","children":[{"id":"231","parent":"230","text":"• Antiplaquetarios (AAS + Clopidogrel).","guid":"kUuvTRQfKlxSIecrURKpaA","children":[]},{"id":"232","parent":"230","text":"• Control estricto de PA.","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"233","parent":"220","text":"📈 Evolución → Pequeño infarto, sin hemorragia, mejoría clínica significativa.","guid":"-10ewehtfggt9LCRlthMNQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"234","parent":"192","text":"3️⃣ Estrategias en\\NAterosclerosis Intracraneal","guid":"pWNX1K3feZr1K4De73MQaQ","children":[{"id":"235","parent":"234","text":"✅ Manejo médico","guid":"criZpRNp-t8ELqBydG8yzQ","children":[{"id":"236","parent":"235","text":"• 🚑 Antiplaquetarios intensivos.","guid":"WHNEpEDO-qogUsrMoyPgQQ","children":[]},{"id":"237","parent":"235","text":"• ⚠️ Control de presión arterial.","guid":"AL6iVFij5ItO4WtaRqoEIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"238","parent":"234","text":"✅ Opciones\\Nendovasculares","guid":"fqNvCGFSZHn99sbWPvAr_w","children":[{"id":"239","parent":"238","text":"• Angioplastia con balón","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"240","parent":"238","text":"• Stenting intracraneal (montado en balón o liberador de fármacos).","guid":"Y70_OHIXOwoDXd21fBPSLQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"234","text":"📌 Situación actual","guid":"TXolzfl2tcQd8MCJNR-BPw","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"🔹 📉 Ensayos previos (SAMMPRIS, VISSIT) no demostraron beneficio del stenting en prevención secundaria.","guid":"J9HzHZAEaLSlgDAsR_tmTA","children":[]},{"id":"243","parent":"241","text":"🔹 🔬 Interés renovado en EVT + stenting en el contexto agudo.","guid":"5LlYz-WVod9ioUbKvOmrqw","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"241","text":"🔹 ❌ Falta de consenso y ensayos clínicos que guíen el manejo óptimo.","guid":"n7UP_gSKgVLrGBWNr0Gs4g","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"245","parent":"0","text":"Optimización de la Recanalización\\Ny Direcciones Futuras","guid":"K21n3Ctaxpb-L7l4WCYCJg","children":[{"id":"246","parent":"245","text":"1️⃣ Desafío: Disociación entre\\NRecanalización y Recuperación Funcional","guid":"r4K19SnLKewU_CSmE4TJJQ","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"📌 >90% éxito en recanalización con EVT, pero solo 50% logran independencia funcional.","guid":"sUm4q1GfL4St6rC2Ue1Q6Q","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"📌 Factores\\Ncontribuyentes:","guid":"LygeKDy0zrQ0Tp1Ub_EO9Q","children":[{"id":"249","parent":"248","text":"• ⚠️ Comorbilidades del paciente (aunque ensayos excluyeron casos con mal pronóstico esperado).","guid":"WfS0G7JZrKu3NK30l_G4_Q","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"248","text":"• ❌ Diferencia entre recanalización y reperfusión → Isquemia-reperfusión puede causar lesión microvascular persistente.","guid":"y27e8gKHdRiXUewhDw-jmg","children":[]},{"id":"251","parent":"248","text":"• 🔬 Mecanismos involucrados","guid":"AuhmRUlRux6kY9U1jFP9Fg","children":[]},{"id":"252","parent":"248","text":"• 🧬 Formación de microtrombos (factor de von Willebrand, colágeno, glicoproteína I).","guid":"C0S_Eooe2GbSIUfIXZlYGA","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"248","text":"• 🔥 Vías inflamatorias no bien caracterizadas en humanos.","guid":"Oebcj_pc866iLb8YUpOAlw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"245","text":"2️⃣ Estrategias para\\NOptimizar Reperfusión","guid":"2OOkxXIvAlTLm8gCqd30fA","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"✅ Terapia\\NIntraarterial Adjunta","guid":"D9erpGQJGWz2LV_SaMIzaA","children":[{"id":"256","parent":"255","text":"• CHOICE Trial → Administración intraarterial de alteplasa post-EVT mejoró resultados clínicos.","guid":"TGdB_IOv4z2qnw4w_QZNWA","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"255","text":"• 📌 Sin aumento de hemorragias → Posible beneficio por lisis de microtrombos distales.","guid":"RYTLgDC9T2XcdXgwfAMZaA","children":[]},{"id":"258","parent":"255","text":"• 🔬 Se necesitan estudios adicionales para confirmación.","guid":"T-aicX4VBopp1i3jgYkXdA","children":[]}]},{"id":"259","parent":"254","text":"✅ Manejo de Presión\\NArterial Post-EVT","guid":"DOY2ef1r1p8HAMQz9QAqZg","children":[{"id":"260","parent":"259","text":"• 📉 Hipotensión y 📈 hipertensión afectan resultados.","guid":"VnDaZiMq8Y9OVSWh3d1Q-A","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"259","text":"• Variabilidad individual → Relacionada con microcirculación cerebral.","guid":"L5LZNXL7k0MQCZDPMVQfoQ","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"259","text":"• 📌 Posible estrategia personalizada de neuroprotección.","guid":"fDpkxirrYVXkHEtHTPCUpw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"263","parent":"245","text":"3️⃣ Futuro de EVT","guid":"rsnBSqVniOHi12hsZlXV8Q","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"📌 Transformación en el manejo del ictus isquémico desde 2015.","guid":"G-cB0wctxmPlbQ2LtqhG3g","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"📌 Investigaciones en curso → Expansión de indicaciones.","guid":"9CHnxGSgvoE-ASyHfGUGRg","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"✅ Áreas clave\\Npara optimización","guid":"Y6qVe9d3Dr_iv3PTArTXSg","children":[{"id":"267","parent":"266","text":"• 🚑 Derivación prehospitalaria → Identificación temprana de pacientes EVT.","guid":"KB5xtnglskbJuR3mgZeBrQ","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"266","text":"• 🏥 Acreditación hospitalaria → Homogeneizar capacidades de EVT.","guid":"KuQHCfrco8Sv0QkvtCT2Uw","children":[]},{"id":"269","parent":"266","text":"• 👩 ⚕️ Formación y certificación de especialistas → Definir estándares.","guid":"Jio3DFn-VIQ20f6RlY1qYQ","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"266","text":"• 💰 Modelos financieros sostenibles → Expansión del acceso a EVT.","guid":"_Yb83UbwXH_lE51_ilKjoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"271","parent":"263","text":"📌 EVT es el área de mayor inversión en neurointervención → Crecimiento acelerado y mejoras tecnológicas constantes.","guid":"Q7kjoPii2U-e0Z4vkTpByQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"272","parent":"245","text":"4️⃣ Puntos Claves","guid":"BKg6irhmSyfEr-LM0wNKNQ","children":[{"id":"273","parent":"272","text":"✔️ EVT es el tratamiento de consenso para oclusión de gran vaso → Impacto clínico significativo.","guid":"LQ6u_wpnsgs_XlNn_Ad2KA","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Ensayos de 2015 validaron EVT como superior al manejo médico.","guid":"98JV_iWIDfw1Bae2aIvKxg","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Neurología es clave en evaluación y derivación de pacientes EVT.","guid":"XIhUqBY0hXHJ-RDakAyLuQ","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Muchos pacientes aún no tienen acceso a EVT → Desafío logístico y organizacional.","guid":"m6MH8_npE3gN-x77waACwg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Falta un sistema de acreditación uniforme para especialistas en EVT.","guid":"967dsusFWFx-qyFian5vMg","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Tiempo crítico en EVT → Derivar pacientes directo a hospitales EVT-capaces puede mejorar resultados.","guid":"Ox2cvavXmu84un7p9VV8Jw","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"272","text":"✔️ CTP en selección tardía es cuestionable → MR CLEAN LATE y RESILIENT Extend evalúan EVT sin CTP.","guid":"bt4pbyeXUsV-61MSdf--_Q","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"272","text":"✔️ rTPA IV sigue recomendado antes de EVT en pacientes elegibles.","guid":"LQMGuOuIu2YX-hPef4ux1Q","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Estudios en China (ATTENTION y BAOCHE) → EVT superior en oclusión de arteria basilar.","guid":"yjhqljl1kJXXhvjLZROdIA","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"272","text":"✔️ DAWN y DEFUSE 3 sugieren cambiar de selección por tiempo a selección por imagen.","guid":"vgguoFUcwzIj20CQG1rgUA","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Ensayos en infartos extensos evaluarán si EVT mejora calidad de vida y no solo reduce discapacidad severa.","guid":"Uj2zHnCdaKTzrvqwvrHG2w","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Tecnología de dispositivos ha sido clave en el éxito de EVT.","guid":"tsNikMr7PzvBaYjoz-WhWA","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"272","text":"✔️ First Pass Effect (FPE) → Nueva métrica estándar para EVT (TICI 3 en primer pase).","guid":"AM8hUPReLQuTQZ-7pW8uSw","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"272","text":"✔️ Aterosclerosis intracraneal como causa de ictus → Evaluación y manejo aún no estandarizados.","guid":"UEKR66Xey-FFaLJbNrBwkQ","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"272","text":"✔️ CHOICE trial sugiere EVT + alteplasa intraarterial como potencial mejora en perfusión microvascular.","guid":"39N2tn1tPdQUxqZ_jAQH7Q","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":287,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"General","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Neurología","filename":"Continuum. Terapia endovascular en Ictus isquemico agudo-2025","id":"map_1402","resolved_references":[]}